OL,5, Former sub-postmaster and campaigner   
OL,6, Alan Bates has said the Post Office    
OL,7, spent 23 years trying to "discredit and
OL,8, silence" him.                          
OL,10,FIn a strongly worded witness statement 
OL,11,Fto the public inquiry into the Horizon 
OL,12,FIT scandal, he accused the Post Office 
OL,13,Fof lying about the accounting system.  
OL,15,FMr Bates told the inquiry that "it was 
OL,16,Fpretty obvious" the Post Office were   
OL,17,F"after me" after he repeatedly raised  
OL,18,Fconcerns about Horizon.                
OL,20,FHis contract was terminated in 2003.   
